    <para id="import-auto-id1172267944090">But we know from (1a) that refractive n<sup>2</sup>= ε/ε<sub>0</sub>. Therefore Dispersion Relation where Refractive Index is expressed as a function of frequency is as follows:</para>
    <figure id="import-auto-id1172267348998">
